description: Gets information about a work team provided by a vendor. It returns details about the subscription with a vendor in the Amazon Web Services Marketplace.

parameters.name: WorkteamArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the subscribed work team to describe.

nested_items.name: SubscribedWorkteam
nested_items.description: A Workteam instance that contains information about the work team.

nested_items.name: WorkteamArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the vendor that you have subscribed.

nested_items.name: MarketplaceTitle
nested_items.description: The title of the service provided by the vendor in the Amazon Marketplace.

nested_items.name: SellerName
nested_items.description: The name of the vendor in the Amazon Marketplace.

nested_items.name: MarketplaceDescription
nested_items.description: The description of the vendor from the Amazon Marketplace.
